Currently it is impossible to search in which space you want to search pages when using the "Include Page" macro. This makes the dropdown showing the result cluttered with results that are irrelevant for me.

Please provide a solution so that the user can choose in which space he wants to search pages, like is done in the "Insert Link" screen. Default the space to search to the space you are currently working on.

Thanks for considering.
